## Third-party components

This project bundles or relies on the following third-party software, each
under its own license. None of these licenses are GPL or copyleft.

### mbedTLS — Apache 2.0
TLS / cryptography library (`deps/mbedtls/`). Used for bundled HTTPS on iOS 5/6
where the system TLS stack can no longer handshake with modern servers.
Source: https://github.com/Mbed-TLS/mbedtls

### SQLite — Public domain
On-device catalog database (`Resources/catalog.db`). Linked dynamically via the
iOS-bundled `libsqlite3.dylib`.
Source: https://sqlite.org/

### Theos — GPLv3 (build system only, not bundled in the IPA)
Cross-compilation toolchain used during development.
Source: https://github.com/theos/theos

## Data sources

The app queries the following public services at runtime. These are not part
of the source code license but are documented here for transparency:

- **stuffed18/ipa-archive-updated** (GitHub Pages, public catalog metadata) —
  https://stuffed18.github.io/ipa-archive-updated
- **archive.org** (public IPA file hosting) — https://archive.org
- **pollinations.ai** (free anonymous LLM endpoint) — https://pollinations.ai

The catalog data and IPA files are hosted by third parties under their own
terms of service. This app is a client that fetches and installs publicly
listed files; it does not redistribute any IPA on its own.
